data.description: Charming ranch in the highly sought after Crichfield school district. Newly remodeled kitchen with new cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops. A semi-open floor plan leads you to 2 different living spaces, with a fireplace. The master bedroom features it's own bathroom and patio doors that lead out to a balcony, overlooking the large wooded fenced in backyard. Check out this large, finished basement with with tons of storage ! This home has a brand new roof with 2 yr warranty, a new A/C and Furnace, a new water pressure tank, and brand new remodeled kitchen as of 2019. Freshly painted and new v flooring. This home wont't last!
data.whatILove: The kitchen is stunning! I love the walk out basement that leads to a fenced in wooded backyard! Great neighborhood!
